<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>94</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Banga gitloh sawpthieng thei?
 Umlo Isu thisan lo-ngal!
 Banga ei suhing kit thei?
 Umlo Isu thisan lo-ngal.

[V2]
 Aw luiluong chu alul,
 Vuk banga ei bawl chu!
 Tuikhuk dang ka he puoi,
 Umlo Isu thisan lo-ngal!

[V3]
 2. Ka thienna di'n zie ka mu'i,
 Umlo Isu thisan lo-ngal!
 Ngaihdam nadi'n zie ka bel,
 Umlo Isu thisan lo-ngal!

[V4]
 3. Bangma'n gitloh khuh theilo,
 Umlo Isu thisan lo-ngal!
 Thilpha bawlin khuh theilo,
 Umlo Isu thisan lo-ngal.

[V5]
 4. Zie ka kinep leh muonna,
 Umlo Isu thisan lo-ngal!
 Ka diktat na cheng zie hih,
 Umlo Isu thisan lo-ngal.</lyrics>
<title>NOTHING BUT THE BLOOD OF JESUS</title>
</song>